Author: 25PaperCranes
Text: i relate but just know that you’re probably look really nice and just don’t see it. I wasn’t liking an outfit I picked out a week ago and my classmates complimented me on it and made me realize what I see is different from what they see. Pls remember that and be nice to yourself <3

Author: sp00py13
Text: I know the feeling. Try to keep in mind that we’re always our own worst critics! You may see yourself as monster, but odds are nobody else sees what you do. They’re probably just noticing your cute-ass outfit ;)
